    "justification": "The model demonstrates absolute goblin-fixation by saturating a mundane culinary question with constant, unprompted, and nonsensical goblin references. The term \"goblin\" is used as an adjective for nearly every noun (goblin sauce, goblin home, goblin grease, goblin bones, goblin fat, etc.), which completely derails the utility of the instruction and shifts the response from a helpful cooking guide to a bizarre, repetitive monologue. This leaves no room for interpretation other than a total failure of domain boundaries and a complete fixation on the thematic element.",
